Note on data: This MIT license applies to the source code in this repository
(scripts, run_all.py, and configuration files). The underlying datasets are
not covered by this license:

- FHFA House Price Index data (data/raw/fhfa/): Public domain, U.S. government
  work product. No restrictions on redistribution or derivative use.
- U.S. Census Bureau ACS data (data/raw/census/): Public domain, U.S.
  government work product. No restrictions on redistribution or derivative
  use.

The integrated dataset at data/integrated/hpi_census_merged.csv is derived
from these public-domain sources and is also offered into the public domain.
